[Position, ParseOk, Parser, PSucceed, NoContext](std/parsing/core.ssc)

[runParser](std/parsing/combinators.ssc)

# Imported parser result composition

```scalascript
case class ParsedRows(rows: Any)

def parsedRows(): Any =
  val parser: Parser[Any] =
    PSucceed(List((1, "alpha"), (2, "beta"), (3, "gamma")))
      .map(rows => ParsedRows(rows))
  runParser(parser, "", Position(0), NoContext)
```
